{"tid":1966141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登式批評性思考","createTime":"2020-04-10T03:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T06:52:37.000Z","uid":275531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ef4df71eb53153b2199360ecde47db1b374902","tid":1966141,"uid":275531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:38:56.000Z","msg":"成日覺得自己諗野高人一等，扮到眾人皆醉我獨醒<br />\n依家最叻就屌同路人<br />\n見人玩動森就屌人跟風，見人食金拱門就屌人扮黃<br />\n其實個個人都有唔同喜好同難處<br />\n下下做少少野就比人屌，個個人都會變得負面，仲邊有士氣打仗<br />\n做得好咪讚囉，對事不對人<br />\n覺得人地做錯既，諗下係咪你自己把尺度得太高<br />\n你有冇見過藍絲黑警屌自己人？"},{"pid":"ab96ec59bed41eae76c9d70501c04ad356e22d91","tid":1966141,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:43:59.000Z","msg":"老實講 興趣思考模式都有分高低既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n考試都有分高低分啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有d人自願做基層教唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有心果d都訂閱蕭生學野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同你睇機場特警 打機咁浪費人生咩<br />\n<br />\n每條路自己選擇唔好埋怨就得"},{"pid":"e786b70638ad791bb9d3eba603ffd0011aee6bb5","tid":1966141,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:14:09.000Z","msg":"阻阻你<br />\n文宣要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［網軍召集］海外手足fb比五毛洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1966095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1966095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"571a416cbbee5b4b6c4a26881523addc42231848","tid":1966141,"uid":245250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"我諗連登仔 唔一定都係同路人<br />\n<br />\n活動一度令連登升格 做左抗爭資訊平台<br />\n<br />\n但事實上連登仔未必全部黃 <br />\n<br />\n而同路人呢個概念都唔係屬於連登仔<br />\n<br />\n連登仔都冇表達打仗係共同目標<br />\n<br />\n佢哋冇需要完全follow <br />\n<br />\n自由意志呢家野控制唔到<br />\n<br />\nDon&rsquo;t expect too much from others <br />\n<br />\nBtw appreciate 你remind大家呢樣野"}]}